<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='924000' id='t-924000'>because I was reading, I was writing,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='927000' id='t-927000'>I was thinking, I was researching.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='929000' id='t-929000'>It was my version</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='931000' id='t-931000'>of my grandfather's hours
of the day alone in his library.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='934000' id='t-934000'>But now all of a sudden
my job is very different,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='937000' id='t-937000'>and my job is to be
out here talking about it,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='940000' id='t-940000'>talking about introversion.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
15:54
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='943000' id='t-943000'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
15:58
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='947000' id='t-947000'>And that's a lot harder for me,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='949000' id='t-949000'>because as honored as I am
