<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='953000' id='t-953000'>this is not my natural milieu.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
16:07
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='956000' id='t-956000'>So I prepared for moments
like these as best I could.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='960000' id='t-960000'>I spent the last year
