<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='962310' id='t-962310'>every chance I could get.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='964000' id='t-964000'>And I call this my &quot;year
of speaking dangerously.&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
16:18
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='967000' id='t-967000'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
16:20
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='969000' id='t-969000'>And that actually helped a lot.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='971000' id='t-971000'>But I'll tell you, what helps even more</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='973000' id='t-973000'>is my sense, my belief, my hope
