<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='982645' id='t-982645'>I mean, we are.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='984000' id='t-984000'>And so I am going to leave you now</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='986000' id='t-986000'>with three calls for action
