</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
16:41
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='990000' id='t-990000'>Number one:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='992000' id='t-992000'>Stop the madness for constant group work.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='994000' id='t-994000'>Just stop it.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
16:47
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='996000' id='t-996000'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
16:50
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='999000' id='t-999000'>Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
16:52
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1001000' id='t-1001000'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
16:54
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1003000' id='t-1003000'>And I want to be clear
about what I'm saying,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1005167' id='t-1005167'>because I deeply believe our offices</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1007000' id='t-1007000'>should be encouraging casual, chatty
