<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1013144' id='t-1013144'>and serendipitously have
an exchange of ideas.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1015359' id='t-1015359'>That is great.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1017000' id='t-1017000'>It's great for introverts
