<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1022153' id='t-1022153'>and much more autonomy at work.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1023700' id='t-1023700'>School, same thing.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1025000' id='t-1025000'>We need to be teaching kids
