</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
17:28
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1037896' id='t-1037896'>Okay, number two: Go to the wilderness.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1040000' id='t-1040000'>Be like Buddha, have your own revelations.</span>
