<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1089478' id='t-1089478'>And that's okay.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1091000' id='t-1091000'>But occasionally, just occasionally,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1093000' id='t-1093000'>I hope you will open up your suitcases
