</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
18:32
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1101000' id='t-1101000'>So I wish you the best
of all possible journeys</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1103263' id='t-1103263'>and the courage to speak softly.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
18:37
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1106000' id='t-1106000'>Thank you very much.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
18:39
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1108000' id='t-1108000'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
18:43
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1112000' id='t-1112000'>Thank you. Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
